import React from "react"
import { Navigation } from "swiper";
import { Swiper, SwiperSlide } from "swiper/react";
import { Image } from "react-bootstrap"

  const imgWidth = [
    "200x",
    "300x",
    "400x",
    "600x",
    "800x",

  return (
    <Swiper
      spaceBetween={20}
      slidesPerView={4}
      slidesPerGroup={4}

  )
}

export default PickCarousel
